handleBuildRequest(NetGaming, boolean) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
It receives a well formed request of build, well formed means that the cell is inside the map, it is needed to check if the build can be done and if all parameters are correct.
handleColorRequest(NetColorPreparation, boolean) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
It receives a well formed request of color, meaning that the color is one of the three available colors, the remote view cannot know if the color is already owned by another player or not, for this reason notifies the ServerController.
handleDivinityRequest(NetDivinityChoice, boolean) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
It receives a well formed request of divinity choice, meaning that the divinity exists or all divinity exists and there aren't duplicates if the player is the challenger and is choosing the gods to play with.
handleGodMessage(NetDivinityChoice) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.controller.SetupManager
This method handles the god requests of all players, it sets the game gods when the challenger chooses them (only if all the gods selected are part of the game), it chooses a player's god if it is free (no one has already selected it) and select the starter when the challenger should select it (only if the request's player is the challenger in its active turn during the right game phase).
handleMoveRequest(NetGaming, boolean) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
It receives a well formed request of a move, well formed means that the cell is inside the map, it is needed to check worker and if is possible to move there.
handleObserverQuit() - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
A player that is an observer has sent a request to quit the game, the request is forwarded to the controller.
handlePositionRequest(NetGameSetup, boolean) - Method in class it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteView
It receives a well formed request of positioning of workers, when with well formed we mean that the position is inside the map.
